		{
			dependencies: [
				"CCA08F9AABBC1CE1"
				"D9E75C6D7E8F9BE0"
			]
			description: ["The LV era is complete. You have electric machines that form, shape, alloy, assemble, and process ore without player input. The Electric Blast Furnace awaits — a multiblock that reaches temperatures impossible with carbon fuel alone. Aluminum at 1700K. Titanium at 1941K. Tungsten at 3600K. Each temperature threshold unlocks a new tier of materials, machines, and circuits. The Cupronickel Coils you wound are the first step. The volt age does not end — it accelerates."]
			id: "DCB19AABBC2DCF14"
